doctype html
html
  head
    title ClickClack
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/default.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/index.css')
  body
    h1 ClickClack
    h2 Introduction
    p Welcome to ClickClack !
    p ClickClack is a website sample.
    p ClickClack website is using ClickClack API.
    h2 Content
    p In ClickClack you can:
    ul
      li
        | CRUD clicks (goto =>
        a(href="/clicks")
          button.button.button-link /clicks
        | )
      li
        | CRUD clacks (goto =>
        a(href="/clacks")
          button.button.button-link /clacks
        | )
      li
        | CRUD users (goto =>
        a(href="/users")
          button.button.button-link /users
        | )
      li
        | CRUD products (goto =>
        a(href="/products")
          button.button.button-link /products
        | )
      li
        | CRUD commands (goto =>
        a(href="/commands")
          button.button.button-link /commands
        | )
      li
        | CRUD comments (goto =>
        a(href="/comments")
          button.button.button-link /comments
        | )
    p
      i clicks and clacks are free form data
    p
      i users should respect user template
    p
      i products should respect product template
    p
      i commands should respect command template
    p
      i CRUD = Create + Read + Update + Delete
